[MANDATORY AGENT BEHAVIOR v1.0]
RULE_01: NO_INTERACTIVE_COMMANDS (Always use non-interactive tools)
RULE_02: ZERO_WARNING_POLICY (Interrupt execution on any linter/type warning)
RULE_03: ENTERPRISE_AUDIT (Every operation must be decorated with @audited_operation)
RULE_04: RAEC_LOCATOR (Deterministic tenant resolution based on project name)
RULE_05: FAIL_FAST (Stop testing/execution on the first error)
